## Phần 2: THIẾT KẾ — 3 API Calls

### Call 1: IDENTIFY (giữ nguyên)
```
Input: cleaned_text
Output: { era, date_range, geography, factions[] }
Retry: 2 lần
Validate: phải có "era" và "factions"
```

### Call 2: PEOPLE (MỚI — thay STEP2A_DESCRIBE_PROMPT)
```
Input: cleaned_text + Call 1 context (era, factions summary)
Output: { factions[] }
  - Mỗi faction: heraldry, primary_colors, armor, weapons,
    role_variants{}, crowd_archetypes{}
  - crowd_archetypes: soldier/civilian_man/civilian_woman = ARRAY 3 variants
    child/noble/clergy = STRING 1 mô tả
Retry: 2 lần
Validate: phải có "factions" với ít nhất 1 entry
```

### Call 3: WORLD (MỚI)
```
Input: cleaned_text + Call 1 context (era, factions summary)
Output: { architecture[], landscape{}, props{}, transport{}, cultural_markers{} }
  - Architecture: exterior, facade, interior, street (KHÔNG lighting)
  - Landscape: terrain, vegetation, water, sky_palette
  - Props: military, household, religious, marketplace, dining, writing
  - Transport: riding, vehicles, pack_animals
  - Cultural_markers: symbols, decorative_motifs, status_indicators
Retry: 2 lần
Validate: phải có "architecture" với ít nhất 1 entry
Rule: "Only describe domains RELEVANT to the script"
```

